.DT
voting room
Discworld room help
voting room

.SH Name
.SI 5
voting room - a place where you can vote on specific issues
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
votes
vote <choice> on <issue>
elections
stand for <position>
second <person> for <position>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a room help file.

Controls the votes for various issues and elections for various positions.
.EP

.SH Commands
.SO 5 12 -22
	vote	Allows you to vote for a specified person or on a specified issue.
	votes	Lists all the current elections and issues up for voting on.
	stand	Propose to stand for a specified position.
	second	Allows you to second someone for a position.  They must be seconded before they are allowed into the actual election.
	elections	Shows the current list of elections.
.EO

.SH Example
.SI 5
> votes
> vote pinkfish on 1
> elections
> stand for womble lover
> second pinkfish for womble lover
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
None
.EP
